            <entry xml:id="entry_ævi" xml:lang="os">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>ævi</orth></form>
                <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                        <q>или</q>
                    </abv:tr><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (в вопросительных
                        оборотах).)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (in
                        questions)</note><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                        <q>or</q>
                    </abv:tr><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (в вопросительных
                        оборотах).)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (in
                        questions)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">союз</note><note
                        type="comment" xml:lang="en">conjunction</note></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>læg ævi ūs?</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>мужчина или женщина?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>(is it) a man or a woman?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"
                            /><biblScope>101</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>ragon æmbīsond wyn zæǧon ævi ærygon?</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>давнее чудо вам рассказывать или недавнее?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>should I tell you about an ancient miracle or about a new one?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОТ"/><biblScope>76</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>qazgæ ma kænūt ævi cy?</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>шутите вы со мной или что?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>are kidding me or what?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОЭ"/><biblScope>I 22</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>cy ū æncondær zæǧæn: barst dyn wænt dæ tærīǧædtæ ævi: syst æmæ
                            cū?</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>что легче сказать: прощаются тебе грехи, или сказать: встань и
                                ходи?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>For whether is easier, to say, Thy sins be forgiven thee; or to say,
                                Arise, and walk?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Матфей"/><biblScope>%i9%i
                            5</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>dæ læg dæ beræ warzuj ævi næ?</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>твой муж тебя очень любит или нет?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>does your husband love you much or not?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MSt."
                            /><biblScope>11%l2%l</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно/ из %iva%i+%ik%i, ср. с одной стороны <mentioned
                        xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>vā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>vā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*vā(β')</w>
                        <gloss><q>или</q></gloss></mentioned>, с другой — <mentioned xml:lang="sla"><lang/>
                        <w>i</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
                        <w>и</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">, соединительный союз</note><note
                            type="comment" xml:lang="en">, coordinating
                        conjunction</note></mentioned>. Для сращения двух союзов ср. хотя бы
                        <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
                        <w>или</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">из %iи%i + %iли%i</note><note
                            type="comment" xml:lang="en">from %ii%i + %ili%i</note></mentioned>.
                    Начальное %iv%i, подверженное отпадению (ср. <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_Acyrūxs"/>), было „спасено“ протетическим %iæ%i-.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">Probably, it is derived from %iva%i+%ik%i, cf. on the one hand
                        <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>vā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>vā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*vā(β')</w>
                        <gloss><q>или</q></gloss></mentioned>, and on the other hand — <mentioned
                        xml:lang="sla"><lang/>
                        <w>i</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
                        <w>i</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">, соединительный союз</note><note
                            type="comment" xml:lang="en">, coordinating
                        conjunction</note></mentioned>. As for the fusion of two conjunctions, cf.
                    at least <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
                        <w>ili</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">из %iи%i + %iли%i</note><note
                            type="comment" xml:lang="en">from %ii%i + %ili%i</note></mentioned>. The
                    initial %iv%i, which is subject to the loss (cf. <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_Acyrūxs"/>), was “saved” by a prothetic %iæ%i-.</etym>
            </entry>
